div.span: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to burn the target. Frozen Pokmon may use this move, in which case they will thaw.
The target will act next this turn, regardless of Speed or move priority. If the target has already acted this turn, this move will fail.

div.div: InfernoSEAR stalks desert wastes, consuming dry brush to fuel its fiery might. It forges paths with triumphs of flame.
